If the pid present, dump it
coredumpctl dump <PID> > /var/tmp/pg-core-PID.core
coredumpctl dump PID -o /var/tmp/pg-core-PID.core

dnf install gdb
gdb /usr/pgsql-14/bin/postgres /var/tmp/pg-core-1981601.core
Analyze core dump file

(gdb) bt



btree
mdread(), mdopen()
smgrextend
visibilitymap
heap_xlog_visible


